    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your country to dominance through the 1800s with a lighthearted countryballs theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose any country throughout the world and form new ones</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/4ec7c3a3f747f2530a07b32b353be079.avif?t=1741366210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras_big/4ec7c3a3f747f2530a07b32b353be079.avif?t=1741366210 width=800 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up your armies and lead them into battle with Real time combat. Nations have different unique units.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/42a528716de95a1228201f8ec8097fb7.poster.avif?t=1741366210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/42a528716de95a1228201f8ec8097fb7.webm?t=1741366210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/42a528716de95a1228201f8ec8097fb7.mp4?t=1741366210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/ac58900f65f845317b52e60b0deeacd6.avif?t=1741366210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras_big/ac58900f65f845317b52e60b0deeacd6.avif?t=1741366210 width=800 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Research new technologies to strengthen your economy and army.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/ed44767c0dddd1ff00be18ad6cb891a5.poster.avif?t=1741366210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/ed44767c0dddd1ff00be18ad6cb891a5.webm?t=1741366210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/ed44767c0dddd1ff00be18ad6cb891a5.mp4?t=1741366210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/27b862fdd78f7172508bcf6f7bc31a1f.avif?t=1741366210\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras_big/27b862fdd78f7172508bcf6f7bc31a1f.avif?t=1741366210 width=800 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new abilities for your armies giving your army an upper hand in battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/20bceebaeda84072cf5b3d52813ae32e.poster.avif?t=1741366210\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/20bceebaeda84072cf5b3d52813ae32e.webm?t=1741366210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/20bceebaeda84072cf5b3d52813ae32e.mp4?t=1741366210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318550/extras/8eef3e953c13476faf3501e155